CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, February 23, 1963, pg.1, reads: "New Minutes Clerk and Family - Shown above are (left to right) Judge Homer S. Brown, friend of the family; Mrs. Alice Scott, sister of the new minutes clerk; Mrs. Williams, wife of the new court official; the appointee; Mrs. Williams, his mother; Andrea Williams, his daughter; Mrs. Edith Johnson, a sister, and Rober E. (Pappy) Williams, brother."
TitMainTitle: New Minutes Clerk Jake Williams in center, with Judge Homer S. Brown, Alice Scott, Mrs. Jake Williams, mother Mrs. Williams, daughter Andrea Williams, Edith Johnson, and Robert E. "Pappy" Williams, standing in courtroom
